main event: An USAF pilot reported seeing a silver aircraft with straight wings flying at high altitude over Victoria, Texas.
interesting points: The object was observed at an estimated altitude between 55,000 to 62,000 feet., The estimated speed of the object was Mach 0.85., The pilot noted a small contrail behind the object., The aircraft was believed to be of the USAF reconnaissance type involved in an experimental test mission., The total observation time was approximately 15 minutes.
sighted object: a silver aircraft with straight wings
